original_title: Disco Biscuits - Live at the Palladium
overview: first Bisco DVD is a two-disc set that will have your living room turned into an energetic trance-fusion throw down! Recorded at The Palladium in Worcester, MA on May 8, 2004, this complete show captures the Biscuits at their brain-bending best.
title: Disco Biscuits - Live at the Palladium
